{"id":"guide/i18n-overview","title":"Angular Internationalization","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"angular-internationalization\" translation-result=\"on\">Angular 國際化<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-overview#angular-internationalization\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Angular Internationalization<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-overview#angular-internationalization\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><em>國際</em>化，有時稱為 i18n，是設計和準備專案，以便在世界各地的不同語言環境使用的過程。<em>本地化</em>是為不同的語言環境建構專案版本的過程。本地化過程包括以下操作。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><em>Internationalization</em>, sometimes referenced as i18n, is the process of designing and preparing your project for use in different locales around the world.\n<em>Localization</em> is the process of building versions of your project for different locales.\nThe localization process includes the following actions.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">提取文字以翻譯成不同的語言</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Extract text for translation into different languages</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">格式化特定語言環境的資料</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Format data for a specific locale</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><em>語言環境</em>標識人們使用特定語言或語言變體的區域。可能的區域包括國家和地理區域。語言環境決定了以下詳細資訊的格式和解析。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A <em>locale</em> identifies a region in which people speak a particular language or language variant.\nPossible regions includes countries and geographical regions.\nA locale determines the formatting and parsing of the following details.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">度量單位，包括日期和時間、數字和貨幣</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Measurement units including date and time, numbers, and currencies</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">翻譯名稱，包括時區、語言和國家</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Translated names including time zones, languages, and countries</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">有關本地化和國際化的快速介紹，請觀看此影片：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">For a quick introduction to localization and internationalization watch this video:</p>\n\n<div class=\"video-container\">\n  <video controls=\"\">\n    <source src=\"assets/videos/Introduction to Internationalization in Angular-KNTN-nsbV7M.webm\" type=\"video/webm\">\n    <source src=\"assets/videos/Introduction to Internationalization in Angular-KNTN-nsbV7M.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    <track src=\"assets/videos/Introduction to Internationalization in Angular-KNTN-nsbV7M.en.vtt\" label=\"English\" kind=\"subtitles\" srclang=\"en\">\n    <track src=\"assets/videos/Introduction to Internationalization in Angular-KNTN-nsbV7M.cn.vtt\" label=\"簡體中文\" kind=\"subtitles\" srclang=\"zh-CN\" default=\"\">\n    <track src=\"assets/videos/Introduction to Internationalization in Angular-KNTN-nsbV7M.tw.vtt\" label=\"正體中文\" kind=\"subtitles\" srclang=\"zh-TW\">\n    <p>注意：本影片不支援 IE 瀏覽器</p>\n  </video>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"learn-about-angular-internationalization\" translation-result=\"on\">瞭解 Angular 國際化<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-overview#learn-about-angular-internationalization\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Learn about Angular internationalization<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-overview#learn-about-angular-internationalization\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Common internationalization tasks\">\n        <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">常見任務</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Common tasks</section>\n    \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何實現與 Angular 國際化有關的常見任務</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to implement many of the common tasks associated with Angular internationalization.</p>\n    \n        <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">常見國際化任務</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Common internationalization tasks</p>\n    \n    </a>\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Optional internationalization tasks\">\n        <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">可選實踐</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Optional practices</section>\n    \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何實現與 Angular 國際化有關的可選實踐</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to implement optional practices associated with Angular internationalization.</p>\n    \n        <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">可選國際化實踐</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Optional internationalization practices</p>\n    \n    </a>\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-example\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Internationalization example\">\n        <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">國際化範例</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Internationalization example</section>\n    \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">檢視一個 Angular 國際化的例子</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Review an example of Angular internationalization.</p>\n    \n        <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">Angular 國際化應用範例</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Example Angular Internationalization application</p>\n    \n    </a>\n</div>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：6/6/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/FormStyle\n - api/common/FormatWidth\n - api/common/NumberFormatStyle\n - api/common/NumberSymbol\n - api/common/Plural\n - api/common/formatCurrency\n - api/common/formatDate\n - api/common/formatNumber\n - api/common/formatPercent\n - api/common/getCurrencySymbol\n - api/common/getLocaleCurrencyName\n - api/common/getLocaleCurrencySymbol\n - api/common/getLocaleDateFormat\n - api/common/getLocaleDateTimeFormat\n - api/common/getLocaleDayNames\n - api/common/getLocaleDayPeriods\n - api/common/getLocaleDirection\n - api/common/getLocaleEraNames\n - api/common/getLocaleExtraDayPeriodRules\n - api/common/getLocaleExtraDayPeriods\n - api/common/getLocaleFirstDayOfWeek\n - api/common/getLocaleId\n - api/common/getLocaleMonthNames\n - api/common/getLocaleNumberFormat\n - api/common/getLocaleNumberSymbol\n - api/common/getLocaleTimeFormat\n - api/common/getLocaleWeekEndRange\n - api/common/getNumberOfCurrencyDigits\n - everyone\n - features\n - guide/architecture-next-steps\n - guide/developer-guide-overview\n - guide/i18n-example\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - guide/i18n-common-overview\n - guide/i18n-example\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview\n - guide/i18n-overview#angular-internationalization\n - guide/i18n-overview#angular-國際化\n - guide/i18n-overview#learn-about-angular-internationalization\n - guide/i18n-overview#瞭解-angular-國際化\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}